1
00:00:51,600 --> 00:00:52,400
Miss Cangyue.

2
00:01:01,760 --> 00:01:03,200
So much medicine.

3
00:01:05,480 --> 00:01:07,520
Which one can knock out the tyrant?

4
00:01:12,760 --> 00:01:13,760
Sleeping potion.

5
00:01:14,320 --> 00:01:15,980
This is too straightforward.

6
00:01:25,520 --> 00:01:26,120
Cangyue.

7
00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:40,640
Why is he here?

8
00:01:44,520 --> 00:01:44,920
He...

9
00:01:45,520 --> 00:01:47,000
Could he have found out?

10
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:50,360
Since I came to this world,

11
00:01:50,960 --> 00:01:53,490
he is the only one to approach me for no reason.

12
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:56,240
But I always feel he's not that simple.

13
00:02:01,240 --> 00:02:02,570
What are you doing here?

14
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:04,720
Me?

15
00:02:05,080 --> 00:02:08,610
The young prince felt the medicine was too bitter a few days ago.

16
00:02:08,720 --> 00:02:10,650
I know a little about pharmacology

17
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:12,560
and should be able to help.

18
00:02:12,960 --> 00:02:14,240
So I came to take a look.

19
00:02:16,079 --> 00:02:17,520
Did you figure out a way?

20
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:24,880
Fang Hai.

21
00:02:26,200 --> 00:02:29,280
Add white quartz together, and then

22
00:02:30,600 --> 00:02:31,930
eat more candied fruit.

23
00:02:34,640 --> 00:02:37,240
What Miss Cangyue said seems to make some sense.

24
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:40,970
However, eating too much candied fruit can easily cause cavities.

25
00:02:41,200 --> 00:02:43,400
It may need further study.

26
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:47,840
Of course.

27
00:02:56,440 --> 00:02:58,240
Good thing I got away with it.

28
00:03:19,480 --> 00:03:23,040
I want to see how far you can go.

29
00:03:30,120 --> 00:03:31,680
Hello, game player.

30
00:03:31,680 --> 00:03:33,040
According to the current progress,

31
00:03:33,040 --> 00:03:34,440
you need to complete

32
00:03:34,440 --> 00:03:36,440
the task objectives of the Holy Maiden of the Moon Shadow Clan as soon as possible,

33
00:03:36,440 --> 00:03:38,840
so that you can get an unexpected surprise.

34
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:41,200
NPC progress 1%.

35
00:03:44,800 --> 00:03:47,200
Your Majesty, the wine you ordered is here.

36
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:32,920
Your Majesty,

37
00:04:33,200 --> 00:04:34,800
the wine you ordered is here.

38
00:04:37,240 --> 00:04:38,240
Come up.

39
00:04:41,200 --> 00:04:41,680
Yes.

40
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:55,640
Does he have some special fetishes?

41
00:04:57,800 --> 00:04:58,880
Hurry up.

42
00:05:10,960 --> 00:05:11,960
Come closer to me.

43
00:05:28,200 --> 00:05:31,200
Once he passes out, I'll stab him in the heart,

44
00:05:31,680 --> 00:05:33,210
and my mission will be over.

45
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:46,409
Want a drink?

46
00:05:48,360 --> 00:05:49,000
No.

47
00:05:49,440 --> 00:05:50,240
I'll feed you.

48
00:05:57,760 --> 00:05:59,560
Your Majesty, please don't.

49
00:06:15,240 --> 00:06:17,480
That's five doses of sleeping drugs.

50
00:06:18,160 --> 00:06:19,600
What if it takes effect?

51
00:06:35,960 --> 00:06:37,440
Your Majesty, no.

52
00:06:38,440 --> 00:06:39,840
[Coughs]

53
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:44,200
Why not?

54
00:06:44,200 --> 00:06:45,280
Not here.

55
00:06:45,880 --> 00:06:47,400
Then where do you want to be?

56
00:06:47,400 --> 00:06:49,130
How about the Imperial Garden?

57
00:06:55,320 --> 00:06:56,200
Your Majesty.

58
00:06:59,120 --> 00:07:01,450
Your Majesty, I am not feeling well today.

59
00:07:02,680 --> 00:07:05,440
Experiencer's character goal 10% complete.

60
00:07:08,760 --> 00:07:11,520
All women in the palace are mine.

61
00:07:12,400 --> 00:07:14,460
Do you think I care about how you feel?

62
00:07:20,080 --> 00:07:22,140
You're this drunk after just one cup.

63
00:07:26,760 --> 00:07:29,000
How is His Majesty doing lately?

64
00:07:29,240 --> 00:07:33,680
His Majesty has taken a fancy to a new maid lately.

65
00:07:33,880 --> 00:07:35,810
He is enjoying himself immensely.

66
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:40,360
He won't even spare the Imperial Garden.

67
00:07:40,360 --> 00:07:41,159
Hahaha.

68
00:07:43,280 --> 00:07:46,640
It's even more absurd than we thought.

69
00:07:46,640 --> 00:07:48,400
Go and add some fuel to the fire.

70
00:07:48,840 --> 00:07:51,640
Being just a tyrant is not enough.

71
00:07:52,680 --> 00:07:54,520
Promiscuous

72
00:07:54,520 --> 00:07:56,080
and ruthless,

73
00:07:56,440 --> 00:08:00,160
that is what the Emperor of Donglin should be like.

74
00:08:00,360 --> 00:08:03,080
Yes, hahaha.

75
00:08:05,280 --> 00:08:08,120
Your Majesty, what are you doing? Your Majesty!

76
00:08:19,600 --> 00:08:20,840
How dare you drug me.

77
00:08:21,600 --> 00:08:24,600
Then I'll turn you into a human swine for my amusement.

78
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:30,730
Thank goodness it was just a dream.

79
00:09:02,920 --> 00:09:03,720
Your Majesty.

80
00:09:04,320 --> 00:09:06,380
The sun must have risen from the west.

81
00:09:06,600 --> 00:09:08,800
I've been by your side for so many years,

82
00:09:08,840 --> 00:09:12,040
but I've never seen any girl who served you

83
00:09:12,040 --> 00:09:14,520
survive on this dragon bed.

84
00:09:14,760 --> 00:09:15,890
She didn't serve me.

85
00:09:15,920 --> 00:09:16,720
What?

86
00:09:17,200 --> 00:09:18,400
She is a lightweight.

87
00:09:18,640 --> 00:09:19,900
One cup and she was out.

88
00:09:20,320 --> 00:09:21,800
I haven't stooped so low

89
00:09:21,800 --> 00:09:23,640
as to be worse than a beast.

90
00:09:26,320 --> 00:09:27,280
That's true.

91
00:09:27,280 --> 00:09:30,080
After all, it's fine wine offered as tribute from the Western Regions.

92
00:09:30,080 --> 00:09:33,680
No one in this world can match Your Majesty's alcohol tolerance.

93
00:09:40,360 --> 00:09:42,560
Isn't he capable of all evil?

94
00:09:42,560 --> 00:09:44,160
How could it be?

95
00:09:48,520 --> 00:09:49,440
Your Majesty.

96
00:09:51,040 --> 00:09:54,570
The Grand Princess has recently taken a liking to another girl.

97
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:58,040
She says the palace cannot be without an Empress for a single day.

98
00:09:58,040 --> 00:10:01,520
She looks like a beauty from the Western Regions.

99
00:10:01,960 --> 00:10:03,440
Why not present her to you?

100
00:10:05,640 --> 00:10:07,760
Ah, no, no.

101
00:10:07,760 --> 00:10:10,800
Good thing Her Royal Highness lives outside the palace.

102
00:10:10,800 --> 00:10:15,240
Otherwise, Your Majesty, you'd have to listen to her nagging every day.

103
00:10:25,360 --> 00:10:28,240
The things my aunt wants to manage...

104
00:10:28,240 --> 00:10:31,440
I can handle more than just this matter.

105
00:11:28,240 --> 00:11:28,840
Zhou Jin.

106
00:11:28,840 --> 00:11:29,040
Cen Zhoujinxuan.

107
00:11:29,040 --> 00:11:31,560
Jin Cen Zhoujin.

108
00:11:39,920 --> 00:11:40,650
Ning Feihai.

109
00:11:40,720 --> 00:11:42,160
Ning Feihai.

110
00:11:44,240 --> 00:11:46,760
Liang Quan Huiyong.

111
00:12:05,680 --> 00:12:06,760
Xu Li.

112
00:12:06,760 --> 00:12:07,600
Xu Li.

113
00:12:07,600 --> 00:12:08,040
Xu Li.

114
00:12:10,920 --> 00:12:11,640
Ming.

115
00:12:11,640 --> 00:12:12,200
Rongming.
